name: Interactive Multi-Game Demo Disc: Version 12
overview: A playable demo disc for the Nintendo GameCube system. Playable games include: 1080° Avalanche Soul Calibur II F-Zero GX Star Wars Rogue Squadron III: Rebel Strike Viewtiful Joe Wallace & Gromit in Project Zoo Billy Hatcher and the Giant Egg Video previews and features include: F-Zero GX 1080° Avalanche Madden NFL 2004 WWE Wrestlemania XIX P.N.03 NHL 2004 Prince of Persia: The Sands of Time
